{"tid":1142861,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"同主管搭的士 佢放咗個屁","createTime":"2019-05-07T11:03:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-07T11:26:58.000Z","uid":43821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"79adba023df0c3b9cb787caea1104ee09d8ef5d9","tid":1142861,"uid":43821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T11:03:06.000Z","msg":"我同我主管住得好近<br />\n<br />\n之前都有試過一齊搭車返屋企<br />\n<br />\n咁啱今日放工嗰陣落大雨<br />\n<br />\n佢就問我一唔一齊搭的士<br />\n<br />\n咁我見大風大雨 行去地鐵站又要10分鐘<br />\n<br />\n廢事搞到成身濕哂 就話好啦<br />\n<br />\n上到的士大家都攰 所以都無講野<br />\n<br />\n突然我聞到車入面有陣勁臭嘅味<br />\n<br />\n我望過去我主管嗰邊 見到佢成個人係到un下un下<br />\n<br />\n我就知佢放咗屁 仲要係勁臭嗰隻<br />\n<br />\n都算 仲要驚死我聞唔到 係咁係到un等啲味散快啲<br />\n<br />\n完全體現到開心Share呢種美德<br />\n<br />\n而家我仲係車 想開窗但出面勁大雨<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />點算好"},{"pid":"44d2f4f1ac0839c42b4caed292ed7f2bb8c582be","tid":1142861,"uid":152630,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T11:08:47.000Z","msg":"主管做野 使唔使你教？"},{"pid":"30f1cb5399289f51b04b562ba44c3fb8183a2990","tid":1142861,"uid":4736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T11:20:20.000Z","msg":"Sorry係我 揸揸下車肚痛"},{"pid":"2494f1f23d98172f231348b138051fd94198e80a","tid":1142861,"uid":43821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"30f1cb5399289f51b04b562ba44c3fb8183a2990","tid":1142861,"uid":4736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T11:20:20.000Z","msg":"Sorry係我 揸揸下車肚痛"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T11:26:58.000Z","msg":"你唔識落車放嘅？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}